snippet.textDisplay: This is insane. Call of Duty going free to play is the direction they desperately needed but have been holding out on. The fact that they are putting all their effort into finally bringing CoD back out of limbo and into the mainstream again after so many years has earned my respect. The song choice perfectly shows they understand and realise what happened in the past and are now making strides to return CoD to its former glory. In my opinion at least this is a really significant release and could be the actual return of a legendary franchise. Please support this game and show the devs that their hard work and the risks they have taken are worth it, and that this new direction for the franchise isn't in vain.
